          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26113513/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26113513/" class="">第39页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57798500/" class=" " title="米兰达">米兰达</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26113513">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">历史不是一面镜子，而是黑板上的记号，可以随时擦去，随时填补。更为可怕的是，一旦涂改了，你找不到证据去证明这是篡改历史的行为。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26113513/">(<span class="">4回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-01 18:07</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">40人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>历史不是一面镜子，而是黑板上的记号，可以随时擦去，随时填补。更为可怕的是，一旦涂改了，你找不到证据去证明这是篡改历史的行为。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







